jobs_results.title: Senior Game Programmer
jobs_results.description:
Gamelogic started out with a small group of gaming enthusiasts and has since expanded into a full-fledged game development studio. As gaming enthusiasts, we are adamant about one thing: which is to have fun. We are experts in having a good time and we hope to offer fellow gamers a chance to unleash their inner child through our awesome games. Our goal is to create innovative casual games that will penetrate the global market. Our team is made up of experienced game designers, programmers and artists and we are constantly looking to nurture the next generation of game developers. When it comes to gaming for us at Gamelogic; the sky’s the limit. ---------------------------------------------------------------------- Title: Senior Game Programmer Responsibilities:
• Brainstorming game concepts, design elements, and specifications with the game design team.
• Leading a team of programmers and set work schedules and deadlines.
• Assist project leaders with statistical testing, and suggest... new methods based on output.
• Selecting suitable game frameworks and translating concepts into clean and efficient code.
• Designing and testing gameplay features and prototypes.
• Generating game scripts and storyboards, as well as animating game characters and objects.
• Contributing to user interface development, as well as the integration of graphic design and audio features.
• Performing tests and implementing validation procedures.
• Documenting the full lifecycle of game development.
• Maintaining code, resolving issues, and performing bug fixes.
• Integrating the latest game industry trends into game designs.
• Working closely with a lead game developer to create task/project deliverables.
• Interface with Quality Assurance, Game Producers, Game Designers and Artists. Requirements:
• Bachelor's degree in computer science, computer engineering, or similar.
• At least 5 years' experience as a game programmer.
• Proficiency in Unity3D.
• Able to work in Windows, Linux and Mac environment.
• In-depth knowledge of full lifecycle game programming and related technologies.
• Highly proficient in programming languages, such as C++, C# and Java.
• Superb analytical and problem-solving skills.
• Excellent communication and collaboration abilities.
• Great organizational and time management skills.
• Able to troubleshoot and solve complex technical issues.
• Highly analytical with excellent written and verbal communication skills.
• Excellent time management skills with the ability to work under pressure to meet tight deadlines.
• Contribute to innovation in game design. Bonus:
• Coursework or certification in game design and development preferred.
• Experience in mobile games development

About UrbanFox Asia:

UrbanFox was unveiled on 24th October 2017, but is not new to the industry. Formerly known as Courex, she was founded in 2009, mainly operating as a Courier service company. Over the years, Courex has evolved into an end-to-end urban logistics expert that provides reliable and economical solutions to help businesses maximize its sales potential. We offer warehousing, multi-channel commerce and delivery solutions.UrbanFox has come a long way since its early days and is now a subsidiary of Keppel Logistics, and works closely with its parent company to leverage on mutual strengths. With Keppel's extensive regional network and UrbanFox’s nimbleness, we are excited about its regional prospects and the growth potential it is able to provide to its customers.We have built a strong foundation of technical know-how and we are constantly exploring new ideas with the aim of adding value to our customers’ businesses. Our team stays up to date on industry’s challenges to help realize customers’ growth ambitions so as to offer solutions that are relevant for different markets around the region.UrbanFox is passionate about building sustainable and innovative solutions that are suitable for businesses of all sizes. We aim to establish long-term partnerships with our customers by providing them with the best experience and value to their business. Accelerate your growth with us
